Cockpuppet
[[Image:Cockpuppet.jpg|frame|right|A regular sockpuppet (left) and a cockpuppet (right) engaging in some [[hott]] [[yiffing]].]]
Unlike a [[sockpuppet]], this puppet is controlled with one's [[penis]] (preferably [[quasidan's penis|a big one]]).
[[fact|Rumor has it]], that while [[Quasidan]] and [[Girlvinyl's vagina]] were on their honeymoon, it was not Quasidan, but actually his cock with a sock, that got [[Girlvinyl]] rid of her [[virginity]], thus making her a [[fat whore]].
Cockpuppetry can also be used for some great [[IRL trolling]] which can spawn lots of [[drama]] and viril envy.

